<Link id="l00342" /><CodeLine lineNumber="342"><Highlight kind="comment">/// Track the current register pressure at some position in the instruction</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00343" /><CodeLine lineNumber="343"><Highlight kind="comment">/// stream, and remember the high water mark within the region traversed. This</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00344" /><CodeLine lineNumber="344"><Highlight kind="comment">/// does not automatically consider live-through ranges. The client may</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00345" /><CodeLine lineNumber="345"><Highlight kind="comment">/// independently adjust for global liveness.</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00346" /><CodeLine lineNumber="346"><Highlight kind="comment">///</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00347" /><CodeLine lineNumber="347"><Highlight kind="comment">/// Each RegPressureTracker only works within a MachineBasicBlock. Pressure can</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00348" /><CodeLine lineNumber="348"><Highlight kind="comment">/// be tracked across a larger region by storing a RegisterPressure result at</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00349" /><CodeLine lineNumber="349"><Highlight kind="comment">/// each block boundary and explicitly adjusting pressure to account for block</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00350" /><CodeLine lineNumber="350"><Highlight kind="comment">/// live-in and live-out register sets.</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00351" /><CodeLine lineNumber="351"><Highlight kind="comment">///</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00352" /><CodeLine lineNumber="352"><Highlight kind="comment">/// RegPressureTracker holds a reference to a RegisterPressure result that it</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00353" /><CodeLine lineNumber="353"><Highlight kind="comment">/// computes incrementally. During downward tracking, P.BottomIdx or P.BottomPos</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00354" /><CodeLine lineNumber="354"><Highlight kind="comment">/// is invalid until it reaches the end of the block or closeRegion() is</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00355" /><CodeLine lineNumber="355"><Highlight kind="comment">/// explicitly called. Similarly, P.TopIdx is invalid during upward</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00356" /><CodeLine lineNumber="356"><Highlight kind="comment">/// tracking. Changing direction has the side effect of closing region, and</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00357" /><CodeLine lineNumber="357"><Highlight kind="comment">/// traversing past TopIdx or BottomIdx reopens it.</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00358" /><CodeLine lineNumber="358" lineLink="/docs/api/classes/llvm/regpressuretracker"><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight><Highlight kind="keyword">class </Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"><a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/regpressuretracker/#a542eddcb7089b3159051d9a1c60eb872">RegPressureTracker</a> &#123;</Highlight></CodeLine>
